OL,3,ECASTLEVANIAGNintendo 64````````````````
OL,5,BKonami has been so quiet in recent     
OL,6,Byears that people with low intellects  
OL,7,Bmight have thought the entire firm had 
OL,8,Bbeen swallowed by a whale.             
OL,10,FHappily, this isn't the case. Though   
OL,11,Fit's stuck its head over the           
OL,12,Fbattlements once or twice recently     
OL,13,F(notably with the PlayStation version  
OL,14,Fof Castlevania, which we really MUST   
OL,15,Fget around to reviewing), the big      
OL,16,FKonami guns will be brought into play  
OL,17,Flater this year.                       
OL,19,BCastlevania on the N64 is coming.      
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````1/4``
OL,21,B    Meet The YouthF140 BPop-offF480    
OL,22,B]MDDOCTOR, MY HEALTH IS REAL BAD p198  
