OL,3,ECASTLEVANIAGNintendo 64````````````````
OL,5,BThe Castlevania lineage dates back to  
OL,6,Bthe 8-bit NES days, when the whip-     
OL,7,Bcracking, vampire-smacking platform    
OL,8,Bstuff was something quite new.         
OL,10,FNowadays, any popular 2D platform game 
OL,11,Fis getting the 3D polygon treatment,   
OL,12,Fand we'd have been sorely disappointed 
OL,13,Fif Konami had stuck to the series'     
OL,14,Foriginal formula.                      
OL,16,BThis time around, you'll get to control
OL,17,Bany of four vampire hunters, who once  
OL,18,Bagain set out to end the scourge of    
OL,19,BDracula and his friend "Greg".         
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````2/4``
OL,21,   B  It's Total Entertainment!F400     
OL,22,B]MDBAMBER - THE RENEGADE MASTER p152   
OL,24,ATV USABSci-FilesCC5 TomorrowFTV Index  
PN,17303
SC,0003
FL,116,117,126,110,1ff,100
OL,1,Rc1,l4|t|h<|Qk5o{%Sx?'ss+a|tk?'ss+o
OL,2,Rz5{5jjjwsQs{5z5S+/#x'' #xt
OL,3,ECASTLEVANIAGNintendo 64````````````````
OL,5,BSet in the mid-to-late 1800s,          
OL,6,BCastlevania begins in a forest, with   
OL,7,Bthe player having to fight past        
OL,8,Bwerewolves and vampire bats to reach   
OL,9,BCastle Dracula.                        
OL,11,FYou'll be able to visit areas more than
OL,12,Fonce, with different aspects coming    
OL,13,Finto play depending on whether it's    
OL,14,Fnight or day.                          
OL,16,BAt the same time, the threat of being  
OL,17,Bbitten by a vampire, and becoming one  
OL,18,Bof their own, is always present. Mmm!  
OL,19,BOut later this year.                   
OL,20,G``````````````````````````````````3/4``
